     (operator precedence bug and X/Y swap)
   o Fixed L1_W_RNA parameter being unused in W_RNA updates
   o Removed dead code in orthogonal H_RNA update
   o Fixed horizontal mode RecError to match optimization objective
   o Extracted shared cell type matching logic (.estimateCelltypes)
   o Added plot.new to NAMESPACE imports

